<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>포켓몬 검색</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .title {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .pokemon-logo {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .search-form {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .search-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .search-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
        }

        .search-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .search-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .error {
            background: #ffe6e6;
            color: #d63031;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            border-left: 4px solid #d63031;
        }

        .help-text {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .examples {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .examples h4 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .example-list {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="pokemon-logo">⚡</div>
    <h1 class="title">포켓몬 검색</h1>

    <form class="search-form" action="/search" method="post">
        <input type="text"
               name="query"
               class="search-input"
               placeholder="포켓몬 이름을 입력하세요 (한글/영어/번호)"
               required>
        <button type="submit" class="search-btn">검색하기</button>
    </form>

    {{#error}}
        <div class="error">
            {{error}}
        </div>
    {{/error}}

    <div class="examples">
        <h4>검색 예시:</h4>
        <div class="example-list">
            한글: 피카츄, 파이리, 꼬부기<br>
            영어: pikachu, charmander, squirtle<br>
            번호: 1, 25, 150
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-text">
        포켓몬의 이름(한글/영어) 또는 도감 번호로 검색할 수 있습니다.<br>
        현재 1세대 포켓몬의 한글 검색을 지원합니다.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>